Style Guide
Typography
Montserrat is an easy-to-read typeface. It works seamlessly across Microsoft
PowerPoint, Google Slides, and is fully supported in PDFs.

guidelines and approved brand assets.

Style Guide
Type setting
Setting up the text hierachy at the early stage makes the design process simpler
and faster later. Moreover, it also ensures the uniformity across the slides.
Weight Size Line Height Usage
Bold 36px 40px Topic Title
Bold 28px 32px Slide Title
Regular 16px 18px Slide Content, Label Button (Big)
Regular 14px 16px Slide Content, Label Button (Medium)
Italic 12px 14px Footnote(Fignote/Source/etc)

Style Guide
Icongraphy
The icons used in this presentation are sourced from PowerPoint's standard icon
library and streamlinehq.com.
Button
Buttons are rounded rectangles with an 8px corner radius
for a modern, clean appearance.
To add subtle depth, the buttons use a layered effect by
placing a slightly offset duplicate shape behind the main
button in a darker (or lighter) shade.
